divs: Sighting DetailsMy grandfather, cousin and I were laying on the hood of our car stargazing one night. out of no where a strange dark obect flew from the horizon at breakneck speed then stopped with in a blink of an eye directly over us(the g force from a stop like that would of ripped any human craft in half.) t seemed to be a ways up. It had 3 lights similar to the lights on our airplanes except they didnt flash.however weird this may sound the sky behind the craft as it flew became ominously dark (even the stars were blacked out.) then it flew impossible fast from a complete stop and flew into the horizon and the blackened sky returned to its normal state after it was gone. I felt as if someone was watching us and i saw something i shouldnt have. i had a strange yet calming feeling the rest of the night.
